    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tempera made using the whole egg, with oils or resins added, having qualities of both egg tempera and oil paint.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000017221/Gottsegen, Manual of Painting Materials (1987)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Témpera fabricada utilizando el huevo entero al que se ha añadido aceites y resinas, con las cualidades de la témpera y de la pintura al óleo.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tempera waarbij het hele ei wordt gebruikt, met toegevoegde oliën of harsen; heeft de eigenschappen van zowel eitempera als olieverf.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>一種將整顆蛋加進油或樹脂製成的蛋彩，兼具蛋彩和油性顏料的特性。 </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
